      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCRUB'S BLUE (1) missed the hat-trick last start when third and beaten 9 lengths (25.81) last time at this track. Solid record here including four wins. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from three starts. Sure to be about the mark. HARA'S OTIS (2) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 1.5 lengths win at Q Straight in a handy 18.80. Fair draw can see a good run and has the ability and in winning form. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Bold showing expected again. MALAWI REBEL (4) finished third (30.24) two back at Q Parklands but out of the placings last time when 8th there. The form from his last run stacks up well. Deserves plenty of respect. HE'S PARANORMAL (7) was in the money last start and poses a threat again.",
